    <h1>UI Coding Standards</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p><br></p>
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image confluence-external-resour=
ce" draggable=3D"false" alt=3D"WDPUI Flow Diagram.jpg" height=3D"400" src=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/download/attachments/1203279551/W=
DPUI%20Flow%20Diagram.jpg?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1663571122867&=
amp;api=3Dv2" data-image-src=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/downl=
oad/attachments/1203279551/WDPUI%20Flow%20Diagram.jpg?version=3D1&amp;modif=
icationDate=3D1663571122867&amp;api=3Dv2"></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>UI Code can be generally divided into 3 sections as shown above</p>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"UICodingStandards-NamingConventions">Naming Conventions</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 68.=
0923%;">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 27.2126%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 33.8296%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 28.6187%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 10.4218%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Recommended File Name</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Recommended Component Name</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Notes</th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Page Component</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx<strong>Page</strong>.tsx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx<strong>Page</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Layout Component&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx<strong>Layout</strong>.tsx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx<strong>Layout</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Container Component</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx<strong>Container</strong>.tsx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx<strong>Container</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Connects to Redux Store</li>
<li>Delegate rendering to Presentational components</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Functional/Renderer Component</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx.tsx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Reusable Component</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx.tsx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Tests</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx.<strong>test</strong>.tsx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Unit Tests</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Styles</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>src/common/<strong>styles</strong>.tsx</p><p>=
src/containers/xxxContainer.<strong>style</strong>.tsx (page level, not reu=
sable)</p><p>eg: PageHeader.<strong>style</strong>.tsx</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Styled</strong>xxx</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Style Component Style definitions</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Types</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>src/common/<strong>types</strong>.ts - local =
types</p><p>src/types/<strong>index</strong>.ts - imported packages</p><p>s=
rc/containers/xxxContainer.<strong>type</strong>.ts (page level, not reusab=
le)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">xxx<strong>Type</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">TypeScript <strong>type</strong> definitions, no=
t <strong>interface</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Constants</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>src/common/<strong>constants</strong>.ts</p><=
p>src/containers/xxxContainer.<strong>constant</strong>.ts (page level, not=
 reusable)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Utils</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>src/common/<strong>utils</strong>.ts</p><p>sr=
c/common/Date.util.ts, src/common/URL.util.ts</p><p>src/containers/xxxConta=
iner.<strong>util</strong>.ts (page level, not reusable)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"UICodingStandards-OtherRecommendations">Other Recommendations</h2=
>
<ul>
<li>All references or checks against string values should be via constant/e=
num</li>
<li>Improve existing code when you change it</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"UICodingStandards-Logging">Logging</h2>
<p>Please think carefully before you log. Make sure you log enough informat=
ion to debug via splunk in case a production issue occurs (error/exception)=
. At the same time be mindful to not log excessively as it causes performan=
ce issues, noisy log (splunk gets costly too) etc. Also NEVER log data, esp=
ecially if it contains PII (Personally Identifiable Data).</p>
<p>MESH Node (EXP API) Log Levels: <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https=
://one.dev1.ui.westpac.com.au/library/docs/mep-node-framework/1.22.2/core/l=
ogging-provider/index.html" rel=3D"nofollow">https://one.dev1.ui.westpac.co=
m.au/library/docs/mep-node-framework/1.22.2/core/logging-provider/index.htm=
l</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
